Package: datimvalidation
Type: Package
Title: External Validation Routines for Data Payloads in DATIM
Version: 1.0.25
Date: 2019-02-15
Author: Jason P. Pickering
Maintainer: Jason P. Pickering <jason.p.pickering@gmail.com>
Description: This package can be used to validate data payloads prior
        to import into DATIM. A range of functions are available to
        validate the structure of the payload in JSON, CSV and XML.
        Full validation of the data including by validation rules are
        also supported.
License: BSD_3_clause + file LICENSE
BugReports:
        https://github.com/jason-p-pickering/datim-validation/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: XML, plyr, jsonlite, stringr, httr, digest, reshape2,
        assertthat, rlist, ISOweek, lubridate, getPass, dplyr
Suggests: doMC, foreach, httptest, knitr, methods, rmarkdown, roxygen2,
        tcltk, testthat, covr, stringi, rprojroot
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
